h_Collins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the world No.1\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"a long break\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American eventually retired to hand Swiatek victory - and following a heated exchange on the court - Collins ripped into the top-seed in her press conference.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999954918791728, \"rank\": 3.634773503782419e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swiatek victory\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"a heated exchange\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"the top-seed\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"her press conference\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I told Iga she did not have to be insincere about, you know, my injury,' Collins said.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.107922302675553e-14, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 1181, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my injury\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is a lot that happens on camera, and there are a lot of people with a ton of charisma and come out and are one way on camera and another way in the locker room.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"a ton\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"charisma\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"one way\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"another way\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"the locker room\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I just have not had the best experience, and I do not really feel like anybody needs to be insincere.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best experience\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They can be the way that they are.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can accept that, and I do not need the fakeness.'\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fakeness\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"pic.twitter.com/vR5Bk80IN5 Swiatek has issued a response and has insisted that she has no idea where Collins is coming from.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pic.twitter.com/vR5Bk80IN5 Swiatek\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"a response\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I will not argue about it, because I have never done anything unpleasant towards her,' Swiatek said.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just wanted to congratulate her on her successful career, because we all know that this is her last year on tour.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her successful career\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"her last year\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"tour\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Honestly, I do not know what she meant because we did not even have any interactions that could have caused her to say that to me.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any interactions\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Generally speaking, during tournaments, when we go out and have time to change our clothes, we are entitled to five minutes.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"our clothes\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"five minutes\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here I asked the lady who escorted me how much time I had.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lady\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not tell me that.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'She replied that they do not count time here and that I should just leave when I feel like it.\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I used this time to change and cool down, and then I returned to the court.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I honestly did not know how much time had passed, but I did not do anything against the rules, so I do not really know what the whole situation was about.'\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how much time\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole situation\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic triathlete makes disgusting revelation after swimming in polluted Paris river ArrowMORE:Olympic gold medallist awkwardly squirms in confrontation over Strictly 2024 'leak' ArrowMORE:Michael Phelps reacts to Leon Marchand's historic Olympic double gold in Paris Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from